title: `Drunk` girl creates ruckus in market in Uttar Pradesh`s Kanpur; video goes viral - WATCH
text:
'Drunk' girl creates ruckus in market in Uttar Pradesh's Kanpur; video goes viral - WATCH By Zee Media Bureau | Last Updated: Friday, February 3, 2017 - 00:33 0 Follow @ZeeNews 
Kanpur: This video is going viral on social media. 
The video shows an allegedly drunk teenage girl creating ruckus in a market of Uttar Pradeshâ€™s Kanpur. 
The incident took place on Tuesday night. 
The girl, who was accompanied by her friend, hit a vehicle while she was riding a two-wheeler. 
The girl was taken to the nearest police station, where her medical tests were conducted.
